title: Nepal plane crash kills at least 50 - army spokesman
text:
Nepal plane crash kills at least 50 - army spokesman Monday, March 12, 2018 - 00:45 
A US-Bangla Airlines flight carrying 71 people crashed at Kathmandu airport killing at least 50 people on Monday, according to an army spokesman. Rough cut (no reporter narration). ▲ Hide Transcript ▶ View Transcript
